TOPIC: Alternative way to install package instead of using yum we will use command or action 
===============================================================================================

vim pranayplaybookfile.yml

---
- hosts: ops
  connection: ssh


  tasks:
    - name: i am installing an scm tool on dev env
      action: yum name=git state=present

