By using playbook how to create a file on any server like slave servers we will write playbook like below
============================================================================================================

vim pranayplaybookfile.yml

---
- hosts: all
  connection: ssh
  
  tasks:
    - name: create a file
      file: path="/root/flm.txt" state=touch
      
    - name: create another file
      file:
        path: "/root/jenkinsfile"
        state: touch

