Now i wnat to create multiple useres
========================================

we can use loops to create multiple users

vim pranayplaybookfile.yml 

---
- hosts: all
  connection: ssh

  tasks:
    - name: create a user
      user: name={{item}} state=present          item(with_items)----------> it is an default varaible in ansible
      with_items:
        - user1
        - user2
        - user3
        - user4

:wq

ansible-playbook pranayplaybookfile.yml -----------> command to execute ansible playbook file


[root@SLAVE-1 ~]# getent passwd---------------> command to use check list of users


