Now I want to change owners of the file and permissions, to change user name, to chnage group name
=========================================================================================================


vim pranayplaybookfile.yml 

---
- hosts: all
  become: yes

  tasks:
    - name: Create Devops directory
      file:
        path: /root/Devops
        state: directory

    - name: Create file inside folder
      file:
        path: /root/Devops/myfile
        state: touch
        owner: pranay
        group: babu
        mode: '0777'

:wq

